changelist.name: Changes
changelist.comment: -- Testing Build 4 -- - New system for car Handling -- Knowed Issue -- - Dont work. (Index Issue)

task.summary: Initial version for CMS21 Multiplayer mod - Allow player to Init the connection with the Server (See serverConsole)
Update to the mod - Allow player to receive Message from server using TCP.
"Huge" update to the mod - Allow Client to Receive and Send Data throught TCP and UDP
RollBack to fix Error - Allow (probably) client to receive and send data throught TCP
--Bug Fixes-- - Added updating from the Mainthread to allow receive Data from server.
Initial GitHub Commit - Early state for player spawning and moving sync (probably work?) - Handle Disconnection
-QuickFix- Remove bin folder from the git

Early Update - 1 - Properly Handle Disconnection - Players Spawning and Movement are Synced (rotation?) !-Knowed Bug-! - connected player list wont work - Other player are invisible - error may appear if a player disconnect and reconnect
-Minor change - Add playerModel

-- Early Update 2 -- - the server side of the mod has been merged with the client side - Allow player to host and connect to the server with a single instance! -- Knowed Bug -- - Can't load asset bundle : result has other player are invisible - server slots status still bugged :wont update on disconnect and maxslot wont display - Index Error while player connect/disconnect (Fix itself after a few seconds?)

-- Early Update 3 -- - Game Updated to 1.0.27 - Handle Player Movement and Rotation - Player has now a model that is rendered InGame - Properly handle other player disconnection - Reworked movement and rotation system (update when moved/rotated > 0.5 -- Bug Fix -- - AssetBundle can now be used - server slots status now work properly - Index error while connecting/disconnecting fixed -- Knowed Bug -- - Changing MelonLoader to last stable (5.7) make game crash due to the mod
-- Git ignore Fix --
-- Git Ignore fix 2 --

-- Early Update 4 -- - Code Refactoring and Reorganised - Handle Inventory (Adding item) - Improved ModGui Backend avoid possible error -- Knowed Bug -- - Only Host can see other Players - Inventory won't sync on connection - Inventory item missing info : BaseUID - Changing MelonLoader to last stable (5.7) make game crash due to the mod

-- Early Update 5 -- - Totaly new Inventory Management ( Testing) adding item with UID work -- Bug Fix -- - All player can see others - Added UID to item Management - Reverted to ML6.0 for compatibility issue
-- Early Update 6 -- - Finally fully Handle inventory (Adding / Removing Item) -- Knowed Bug -- - Possible Error caused by desync from item UID (p1 lastUid:1008, p2 lastUid:978)

-- Early Update 8 -- - Major Refactor of "playerManagement" - playerManagement renamed to "MPGameManager" - Fully Handle Part (RealTime Update) -- Knowed Bug -- - Possible error comming when a part is updated ( send -> receive -> send receive) - Not tested with multiple car -- Removed -- - Engine part Handling - Suspension part Handling

-- Pre-Beta 1 -- - Fully Handle EnginePart - Fully Handle SuspensionPart -- Knowed bug -- - Possible error comming when a part is updated ( send -> receive -> send receive) - Not tested with multiple car - Possible Error caused by desync from item UID (p1 lastUid:1008, p2 lastUid:978) - server slot not update properly - Disconnecting from a server make you need to relaunch game to connect again - Host cannot stop hosting (crash) - client need to connect twice before being connected to server - client crash if wrong ip adress is typed -- Bug Fixed -- - Insane freeze when loading seem fixed?

-- Pre-Release 0 -- - No Addition -- Knowed Bug -- - Possible Error caused by desync from item UID (p1 lastUid:1008, p2 lastUid:978) - server slot not update properly - Disconnecting from a server make you need to relaunch game to connect again - Host cannot stop hosting (crash) - client need to connect twice before being connected to server - client crash if wrong ip adress is typed -- Bug Fix -- - Insane Freeze when car spawn. - Useless part update when received. - Multiple car Handling Fixed.

-- Pre-Release 0 Bug Fix 1-- - No Addition -- Bug Fix -- - Server slot now Update Properly - Disconnecting now no longer broke the mod - Host can now stop/start without crash -- Knowed Bug -- - client need to connect twice before being connected to server - client crash if wrong ip adress is typed
